  "Invite a friend, get 1 week free Premium" - viral growth engine with tracking codes.    
                                                                                           
  4. Offline Downloads (PWA/Mobile)                                                        
                                                                                           
  Let premium users download content for offline viewing. Major differentiator.            
                                                                                           
  ---                                                                                      
