  5. Match Predictions & Leaderboards                                                      
                                                                                           
  - Let users predict match scores before kickoff                                          
  - Weekly/monthly leaderboards with prizes                                                
  - Gamification increases daily active users                                              
                                                                                           
  6. User Reviews & Ratings                                                                
                                                                                           
  - Let users rate movies/series (1-5 stars)                                               
  - Show community ratings alongside TMDB ratings                                          
  - "95% of users liked this"                                                              
                                                                                           
  7. Personalized Recommendations                                                          
                                                                                           
  - "Because you watched X, you might like Y"                                              
  - Machine learning based on watch history                                                
  - "Trending in Somalia" section                                                          
                                                                                           
  8. Stories/Reels Feed                                                                    
                                                                                           
  Expand your Shorts section into a TikTok-style vertical feed with swipe navigation. High 
  engagement format.                                                                       
                                                                                           
