  My Recommendation: Vercel                                                                
                                                                                           
  Why Vercel Wins for Your Project                                                         
  Factor: Next.js optimization                                                             
  Vercel: Built by same team, perfect integration                                          
  AWS: Manual configuration                                                                
  ────────────────────────────────────────                                                 
  Factor: Deployment                                                                       
  Vercel: git push = deployed                                                              
  AWS: Complex CI/CD setup                                                                 
  ────────────────────────────────────────                                                 
  Factor: Edge Network                                                                     
  Vercel: 100+ global edge locations                                                       
  AWS: Need CloudFront setup                                                               
  ────────────────────────────────────────                                                 
  Factor: Convex compatibility                                                             
  Vercel: Seamless                                                                         
  AWS: Same (Convex is separate)                                                           
  ────────────────────────────────────────                                                 
  Factor: Time to deploy                                                                   
  Vercel: 5 minutes                                                                        
  AWS: Hours/days                                                                          
  ────────────────────────────────────────                                                 
  Factor: Maintenance                                                                      
  Vercel: Zero                                                                             
  AWS: You manage everything                                                               
  ────────────────────────────────────────                                                 
  Factor: Cost at your scale                                                               
  Vercel: ~$20-50/mo                                                                       
  AWS: Similar or higher                                                                   
  ────────────────────────────────────────                                                 
  Factor: SSL/Domain                                                                       
  Vercel: Automatic                                                                        
  AWS: Manual ACM setup                                                                    
  ---                                                                                      
  Why NOT AWS for You                                                                      
                                                                                           
  1. Overkill - You don't self-host videos, Convex handles your backend. AWS power is      
  wasted.                                                                                  
  2. Complexity - AWS requires:                                                            
    - EC2 or ECS/Fargate for servers                                                       
    - S3 for assets                                                                        
    - CloudFront for CDN                                                                   
    - Route53 for DNS                                                                      
    - ACM for SSL                                                                          
    - Load balancers                                                                       
    - IAM permissions                                                                      
    - VPC configuration                                                                    
                                                                                           
  That's weeks of DevOps work.                                                             
  3. Your backend is Convex - The main reason to use AWS would be custom backend logic, but
   Convex already handles:                                                                 
    - Database                                                                             
    - Real-time subscriptions                                                              
    - Serverless functions                                                                 
    - File storage                                                                         
  4. Cost unpredictability - AWS bills can surprise you. Vercel is predictable.            
                                                                                           
  ---                                                                                      
  When AWS Would Make Sense                                                                
                                                                                           
  - Self-hosting video files (S3 + CloudFront)                                             
  - Custom transcoding pipeline (MediaConvert)                                             
  - Heavy server-side processing                                                           
  - Multi-region database (but Convex handles this)                                        
  - Enterprise compliance requirements                                                     
                                                                                           
  None of these apply to your current architecture.                                        
                                                                                           
