⏺ Ah, Lightsail specifically! That's a fairer comparison. Let me break it down:            
                                                                                           
  ---                                                                                      
  AWS Lightsail vs Vercel                                                                  
  ┌─────────────────┬───────────────────────────┬────────────────────────┐                 
  │     Factor      │          Vercel           │     AWS Lightsail      │                 
  ├─────────────────┼───────────────────────────┼────────────────────────┤                 
  │ Type            │ Serverless Platform       │ VPS (Virtual Server)   │                 
  ├─────────────────┼───────────────────────────┼────────────────────────┤                 
  │ Pricing         │ $20/mo Pro                │ $5-40/mo fixed         │                 
  ├─────────────────┼───────────────────────────┼────────────────────────┤                 
  │ Next.js Support │ Native, optimized         │ Manual setup (Node.js) │                 
  ├─────────────────┼───────────────────────────┼────────────────────────┤                 
  │ Scaling         │ Automatic                 │ Manual (upgrade plan)  │                 
  ├─────────────────┼───────────────────────────┼────────────────────────┤                 
  │ Edge/CDN        │ Built-in (100+ locations) │ Add CloudFront ($)     │                 
  ├─────────────────┼───────────────────────────┼────────────────────────┤                 
  │ SSL             │ Automatic                 │ Manual (Let's Encrypt) │                 
  ├─────────────────┼───────────────────────────┼────────────────────────┤                 
  │ Deployment      │ git push                  │ SSH + PM2/Docker       │                 
  ├─────────────────┼───────────────────────────┼────────────────────────┤                 
  │ Server Access   │ No (serverless)           │ Full SSH access        │                 
  ├─────────────────┼───────────────────────────┼────────────────────────┤                 
  │ Downtime        │ Zero-downtime deploys     │ Brief during restarts  │                 
  └─────────────────┴───────────────────────────┴────────────────────────┘                 
  ---                                                                                      
  Lightsail Pricing (Fixed)                                                                
  ┌────────┬───────┬─────┬─────────┬──────────┐                                            
  │  Plan  │  RAM  │ CPU │ Storage │  Price   │                                            
  ├────────┼───────┼─────┼─────────┼──────────┤                                            
  │ Basic  │ 512MB │ 1   │ 20GB    │ $3.50/mo │                                            
  ├────────┼───────┼─────┼─────────┼──────────┤                                            
  │ Small  │ 1GB   │ 1   │ 40GB    │ $5/mo    │                                            
  ├────────┼───────┼─────┼─────────┼──────────┤                                            
  │ Medium │ 2GB   │ 1   │ 60GB    │ $10/mo   │                                            
  ├────────┼───────┼─────┼─────────┼──────────┤                                            
  │ Large  │ 4GB   │ 2   │ 80GB    │ $20/mo   │                                            
  ├────────┼───────┼─────┼─────────┼──────────┤                                            
  │ XL     │ 8GB   │ 2   │ 160GB   │ $40/mo   │                                            
  └────────┴───────┴─────┴─────────┴──────────┘                                            
  ---                                                                                      
  My Recommendation                                                                        
                                                                                           
  Choose Vercel if:                                                                        
                                                                                           
  - You want zero DevOps work                                                              
  - Fast iteration is priority                                                             
  - You value automatic scaling                                                            
  - Your traffic is unpredictable (viral moments)                                          
  - You want best Next.js performance (ISR, Edge Functions)                                
                                                                                           
  Choose Lightsail if:                                                                     
                                                                                           
  - You want fixed predictable cost ($5-20/mo)                                             
  - You're comfortable with server management                                              
  - You need SSH access for other services                                                 
  - You want to run multiple apps on one server                                            
  - Budget is very tight                                                                   
                                                                                           
  ---                                                                                      
  The Real Issue with Lightsail + Next.js                                                  
                                                                                           
  Lightsail Challenges:                                                                    
  ├── No automatic Next.js optimizations                                                   
  ├── No built-in CDN (pay extra for CloudFront)                                           
  ├── No edge functions (middleware runs on origin)                                        
  ├── Manual SSL renewal setup                                                             
  ├── PM2/Docker setup required                                                            
  ├── No zero-downtime deploys (needs setup)                                               
  └── Server restarts = brief downtime                                                     
                                                                                           
  Your Next.js 16 app uses:                                                                
  - App Router ✓                                                                           
  - Server Components ✓                                                                    
  - Middleware ✓                                                                           
  - Dynamic routes ✓                                                                       
                                                                                           
  These features are optimized automatically on Vercel but require manual tuning on        
  Lightsail.                                                                               
                                                                                           
