  ---                                                                                      
  If You Choose Lightsail                                                                  
                                                                                           
  You'd need to set up:                                                                    
                                                                                           
  # On Lightsail instance                                                                  
  sudo apt update                                                                          
  sudo apt install nodejs npm nginx certbot                                                
                                                                                           
  # Clone and build                                                                        
  git clone your-repo                                                                      
  npm install                                                                              
  npm run build                                                                            
                                                                                           
  # PM2 for process management                                                             
  npm install -g pm2                                                                       
  pm2 start npm --name "fanbroj" -- start                                                  
  pm2 startup                                                                              
  pm2 save                                                                                 
                                                                                           
  # Nginx reverse proxy                                                                    
  # SSL with Certbot                                                                       
  # GitHub webhook for auto-deploy (optional)                                              
                                                                                           
  That's 2-4 hours of setup + ongoing maintenance.                                         
                                                                                           
